            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan> Porcius <lb n="2"/>Verus <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>proc</abbr><ex>urator</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> me posu<lb break="no" n="2"/>it
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Mithrasrelief; Z. 1-5 stehen links, Z. 6 u. 7 rechts der Stiertötungsszene, flankiert von Cautopates und Cautes. Material: Bacherermarmor.</p>
            </div>
